@H_Miss88 In the winter every 3-4 weeks ish or whenever the top layer of the soil is dry and in summer 2 litres of water every 10-14 days or again when the soil is dry. New leaves appear March-sept ish and then they go dormant in the winter!
@H_Miss88 Don’t overwater him and turn him regularly so he grows evenly and doesn’t fall lop-sided! Also they don’t like direct sunlight. Cheese plants love to be neglected 🤣
